---
title: One Pot Korma Style Baked Rice with Pepper, Peas and Yoghurt
description: Our One Pot Korma Style Baked Rice is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R42_W28_UK_R16584-3_Main_low-b6f69c0e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/663a4966db4284dbea8d072d-en-GB.pdf
